SOLD BY WINSTON TOWERS 300 ASSOCIATION TO GROUP OF FRIENDS, LLC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
WILMINGTON SAVINGS FUND SOCIETY, FSB, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2099 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 09, 2017 LAGOA, EMAS and SCALES, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that appellee's motion to dismiss appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed. See Kogan v. Mildenberger, 127 So. 3d 831 (Fla. 3d DCA 2013) ; Fascetti v. Fascetti, 795 So. 2d 1094 (Fla. 4th DCA 2001).
